		<title>优先股: 定义, 4种类型, 如何运作 &#038; 真实案例</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/analysis/trading-strategies/preference-shares</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 05:57:40 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[交易策略]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[stocks]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新手交易策略]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.atfx.com/?p=25466</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[目录: 1. 什么是优先股？ 2. 优先股的4种类型 3. 优先股的利与弊 4. 优先股与普通股 5. 了解优 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p dir="ltr"><strong>目录:</strong></p>
<p dir="ltr"><a href="#what-is-preferred-stock" rel="noopener">1. 什么是优先股？</a></p>
<p dir="ltr"><a href="#types-of-preferred-stock" rel="noopener">2. 优先股的4种类型</a></p>
<p dir="ltr"><a href="#pros-and-cons-of-preferred-stock" rel="noopener">3. 优先股的利与弊</a></p>
<p dir="ltr"><a href="#preferred-stock-vs-common-stock" rel="noopener">4. 优先股与普通股</a></p>
